{"tid":2152966,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美參議員麥康奈爾談黎智英被捕：繼區議會變天後，中共迅速扼殺香港自由","createTime":"2020-08-12T09:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T10:38:16.000Z","uid":70063,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a0e491cb6fdcceafde195b6a63d5f2cb335a4281","tid":2152966,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T09:25:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LA5HY4Tbt5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLA5HY4Tbt5g&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf9E6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=f2689a82\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LA5HY4Tbt5g</a><br />\n<br />\n美國參議院多數黨領袖麥康奈爾（Mitch McConnell）周一在參議院發言時，形容壹傳媒創辦人黎智英被捕「令人不安」，他讚揚黎智英大半生致力推動思想和言論自由的價值，表示美國及熱愛自由的國家都與黎智英和所有被中共打壓的和平示威者並肩。<br />\n<br />\n麥康奈爾表示，香港為捍衛民主自治而持續鬥爭，本周卻收到更加令人不安的消息&mdash;&mdash;身為香港最有名的民主倡議者之一的黎智英，昨日以違反北京實施所謂的國安法被捕。<br />\n<br />\n他說繼去年的區議會選舉有數百萬人投票創下歷史，壓倒性讓中國國家主席習近平偏好的候選人落選後，中共便迅速行動扼殺香港的表達自由。<br />\n<br />\n麥康奈爾形容黎智英一直在香港蓬勃的大眾傳媒及出版世界擔當先鋒，畢生大部份時間致力推動中共最抗拒的思想和言論自由價值，「致參議院，這個國家及世界各地熱愛自由的國家都與黎智英並肩，支持所有被中共打壓的和平示威者」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200811/WJHOVR3C2YGJ7UWD7IMARYWSSM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200811%2FWJHOVR3C2YGJ7UWD7IMARYWSSM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWf9E6lK5ze4L1B2G6UiHaG78%3D&h=65277aff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200811%2FWJHOVR3C2YGJ7UWD7IMARYWSSM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=06b43018\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200811/WJHOVR3C2YGJ7UWD7IMARYWSSM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"57fd007fe15097be0d57457b81691739e0549f1b","tid":2152966,"uid":170143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}